comments: Lowry (TOR) brushes Walker's (BOS) right leg and marginal contact occurs as Walker loses control of the ball after his gather.
VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental body contact with Theis (BOS) as they each attempt to retrieve the ball.
Ibaka (TOR) reaches in and makes marginal contact occurs with Theis' (BOS) right arm on the play.
Tatum (BOS) briefly has his arms around Ibaka's (TOR) upper half before correcting.
Siakam (TOR) makes incidental contact with Brown's (BOS) backside and right arm as he taps the ball toward the perimeter during the rebound.
Brown (BOS) rests his hands on Siakam's (TOR) backside and marginal contact occurs as Siakam dribbles into the lane. Brown then cleanly ties up Siakam and a jump ball is correctly assessed.
Walker (BOS) and VanVleet (TOR) engage and disengage with one another as the jump ball occurs. VanVleet then uses his forearm to make clean contact with the ball as they each attempt to gain control.
Tatum (BOS) is moving slightly toward VanVleet (TOR) as body contact occurs following the jump ball, which Tatum absorbs.
Lowry (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position and turns slightly toward Tatum (BOS) as contact occurs during the pick, but it is marginal.
Tatum (BOS) extends his off-arm into Anunoby's (TOR) front and initiates contact that creates space at the end of the drive.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Brown (BOS) turns into Lowry (TOR) and initiates contact to his side after his gather.
Walker (BOS) makes slight contact with Ibaka's (TOR) right arm as Walker shifts his momentum and steps backward at the end of the drive.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Brown's (BOS) path and does not deliver the contact.
Smart (BOS) is moving laterally as body contact is initiated by Siakam (TOR) after his gather, which Smart absorbs. Smart then uses his right forearm to cleanly strip Siakam of the ball.
Anunoby (TOR) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of TOR ball stood.
Ibaka (TOR) is firming up in his screening position in Brown's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact as it is made.
Siakam's (TOR) left heel steps out of bounds on the sideline after he receives the pass.
Anunoby (TOR) dives in an attempt to retrieve the ball and makes marginal contact with Walker's (BOS) backside.
VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact with his arm to Walker's (BOS) front near halfcourt.
Lowry (TOR) rests his right hand/forearm on Smart's (BOS) front as marginal contact occurs during rebounding.
Ibaka (TOR) and Smart (BOS) make incidental body contact with one another during rebounding.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
